title: Re: Knowing The Track, Walking The Track
content:
Sorry to revive an old thread, but I didn't think it'd be worth creating a whole new thread for one new mix.

For those who don't know, Dwelling of Duels is a monthly game remix contest... except that the main instrument in each remix must be played, not programmed. This month, the theme was PC Games, and someone (I don't know who yet - they remain anonymous during the voting process) submitted a great piano mix of Wednesday at the Beach, from Keen 5.

To find it, go to [url=http://dod.vgmix.com/current.php]dod.vgmix.com/current.php[/url] ... (or, if you're reading this after the voting is finished, go to the Past Duels section, and look for August 2007)

content: Good find. 'Tis a very nice piano adaptation.
